java.lang.Object

DelegatingMetricsConfiguration
public class MetricsConfigurationSupport
extends Object
implements org.springframework.context.annotation.ImportAware

This is the main class providing the configuration behind the Metrics Java config. It is typically imported by adding @EnableMetrics to an application @Configuration class.

Since:
3.0

Ryan Tenney
